data.description: *PRICE REDUCED!!* Welcome to your beautiful slice of East Layton in the quiet Oak Forest Subdivision. This home features an extremely manageable and fully private yard with balconies to enjoy your mountain views. Quick access to highway 89, shopping, HAFB, hiking, and skiing. Nestle in to this five bedroom three bath home and get cozy by one of the three fireplaces.   Ramp is not attached to home. Updates to note are a two year old roof with warranty, new composite deck out back, new A/C and heater, newer water heater, and new garage door opener. Plenty of room to entertain upstairs or down and ample storage as well. You really can't find a floor plan with this kind of character anymore. Come make this home your own and have peace of mind with a home warranty included.
